id: pm-5oti
title: Auto Release retries branch push after main advances
description: Scheduled Auto Release run 27743290726 passed release gates on 2026-06-18 but failed at git push origin HEAD because origin/main advanced during the long gate window. Add release-pipeline retry/rebase handling so daily auto-release can publish when the release commit can be replayed cleanly.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: "area:ci","area:release",github-actions,reliability
created_at: "2026-06-18T13:29:07.198Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-18T14:11:35.125Z"
author: codex-implementation
parent: pm-u9d0
resolution: "Auto Release now pushes the release commit and tag atomically, rebases on origin/main when the first push is rejected because main advanced, retargets the local tag, and retries the atomic push."
expected_result: A scheduled release whose gates pass should recover from a clean origin/main fast-forward race instead of failing after creating the local release commit.
actual_result: "Unit coverage exercises successful retry, non-retryable failure, and retry failure paths; Sentry/telemetry gate was healthy and full coverage passed at 100/100/100/100."
comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-18T13:29:07.198Z",codex-implementation,"Duplicate check: pm search 'Auto Release non-fast-forward push main advanced git push origin HEAD' found historical release issues and the open Sentry-gate item pm-nb08, but no all-status item for the non-fast-forward branch push failure from run 27743290726. This item tracks that separate push-race defect."
  "2026-06-18T13:30:46.534Z",codex-implementation,"Implementation link: bundled with pm-hl9y in this PR; pm deps is read-only in the current command surface, so the relationship is recorded here and both items share PR evidence."
  "2026-06-18T13:45:11.620Z",codex-implementation,"Evidence: release pipeline spec passed (30 tests), linked pm test --run passed in sandbox, full coverage passed at 100/100/100/100, latest scheduled Auto Release failure 27743290726 was non-fast-forward push, Sentry/telemetry gate returned ok with 0 blocking Sentry issues."
  "2026-06-18T14:00:00.321Z",codex-implementation,"Review follow-up: addressed Gemini/CodeRabbit feedback by passing git identity env through release push/rebase commands, aborting failed rebases, broadening branch-behind detection, and adding immediate-success plus rebase-failure tests. Re-ran release spec, typecheck, and full coverage at 100/100/100/100."
  "2026-06-18T14:06:47.771Z",codex-implementation,"Review follow-up: addressed Gemini's latest branch-behind detector finding by removing the generic 'failed to push some refs' retry signal and adding a regression that permission failures with that Git trailer fail immediately without fetch/rebase. Focused release spec passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.spec.ts (32 tests)."
  "2026-06-18T14:11:35.125Z",codex-implementation,"Evidence after latest Gemini fix: full coverage passed at 100/100/100/100 (4546 tests), pnpm typecheck passed, pnpm changelog:pm:check was unchanged using pm-changelog 2026.6.14, and pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift passed with only pre-existing validate_resolution_missing_fields:198 warnings and history_drift ok."
